description: Sunday Open Canceled! Offer Accepted!!! Located in the heart of City Point, this thoughtfully updated 2-bedroom + office, 1-bath home blends classic South Boston charm with creative modern updates.  The renovated kitchen features quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, wine storage and plenty of cabinet space—ideal for cooking at home or entertaining friends. The bathroom has been fully updated with clean, contemporary finishes, a freestanding tub and a walk-in shower. A bonus office offers the perfect WFH setup, walk in closet, or a cozy guest space.Enjoy your private deck, and extra private storage in the basement.  Tucked into one of Southie’s most desirable pockets, you're just blocks from M Street Beach, Medal of Honor Park, and all the dining and coffee spots along East Broadway. Don’t miss your chance to live in one of South Boston’s most sought-after neighborhoods!
